      • confirmIngredient

        public void confirmIngredient()
        This method is run when the confirm button is pressed on the ingredient form, the method then gets the relevant information from the user input, creates a new ingredient from it, and then adds it to an instance of Business. It also gives back informational feedback to the user to inform them that the ingredient has been added successfully.

      • fieldsAreValid

        public boolean fieldsAreValid()
        Checks the validity of every TextField. This includes empty fields, invalid prices, and invalid quantities.
        Returns:
        A boolean, true if all fields are valid, false otherwise.
